text: Wes Kremer (born November 27, 1989) is an American professional skateboarder. Kremer was named Skater of the Year in 2014 by Thrasher Magazine. == Early life == Kremer was born in Tokyo while his American parents were living there for work. ==References== Category:American skateboarders Category:Sportspeople from Tokyo Metropolis Category:1989 births Category:Living people
title: Wes Kremer
